=== Installation ===
Simply copying the .ttf files to /usr/share/fonts and running fc-cache on it works.
Here are the detail instructions:
	# tar -xvf samyak-fonts-<version>
 	# cd samyak-fonts-<version>
	//Do as a root user
	# cp <language>/Samyak-<language>.ttf /usr/share/fonts/<directory of your choice> 
	//Recommended directory name "Samyak"
	# cd /usr/share/fonts/<directory of your choice>
	# fc-cache

